articles.title: WNBA All-Star 2025: Napheesa Collier scores record 36 points in blowout of Caitlin Clark's squad - Yahoo Sports
articles.description: Team Collier had its fun in a runaway win over Team Clark in Indianapolis.
articles.content:
The WNBA All-Star Game that featured Caitlin Clark everywhere but on the court resulted in a blowout win for Napheesa Collier's team, and a record for the Minnesota Lynx star.
